**NodeJs Basic**

* What is NodeJs
->NoteJs is a Runtime enviroment for javaScript.

"Rayan Dahl" Create NodeJs using 'Chrome V8 engine + c++' code and create NodeJs.

JS engine in Chrome= V8 Engine 
FireFox= Spidermonkey

Using nodejs we can use js on browser and our code compiler.

NodeJs is totally Js code and consept.

**Install NodeJS**
Download Link - https://nodejs.org/en/download ( LTS )

**Code Compiler (VS Code)**
Download Link - https://code.visualstudio.com/download  

After download this run 'node --v' to check the current Node js Version on your machine.

